title: Sonichu (Complete)
description:
The TRUE and HONEST Sonichu, issues #0 to (what there is of) #11, plus specials. All in its (hopefully) uncensored and unedited glory. It is my gift to you. You're welcome.

Note: This is an updated version of an anonymous torrent I had uploaded a while ago. I was recently skimming through the CBRs to discover that I actually screwed up when adding a couple pages in issue #8. Of course, making any changes would require me to redo the entire torrent, so I did just that.

CBR reader: http://www.cdisplayex.com/
